message.body: Hey Lindsey! Do you know if Dave is in today/if we have a meeting today?
He is out so I am going to assume we have no meeting. Anu hasn't said anything to me about it today.
Lovely. I have to come in today to print something SO I will likely see you anyways :)
Yay!!! We never see each other anymore.
I knooooow it is le bummer. I am having a costume party in November that everyone in the world is invited to so hopefully you can attend! (Once I grind out details)
Yeah!! I am gonna be Rosanne.
